word_mean_info__list.difference: 常指最重要、价值最高的东西，也可以表示最佳、最典型或最高的人或物。
多用于指对抽象事物的主观评估，有时含夸大、自负的意味。
指通过精心挑选达到水平，尤指罕见或品质精良的商品。

bilingual.source: The internet has become the country's prime entertainment service.
bilingual.target: 在中国，互联网已经成为主要的娱乐方式。

bilingual.source: Our market analysis tells us our prime users will be between 40 to 60.
bilingual.target: 我们的市场分析告诉我们，我们产品主要的使用者年纪将在40至60岁。

bilingual.source: Today he is the prime mover in China's most prestigious think tank.
bilingual.target: 今天他是中国最有声望的智库中主要的活动家。

bilingual.source: Two seperate 2-story buildings on one lot in prime location in Alhambra.
bilingual.target: 两个独立的两层房屋在主要的地段位置在阿罕布拉市。

bilingual.source: Utmost efficiency in the design and manufacture, of turbomachinery is a prime competitive factor.
bilingual.target: 在涡轮机设计和制造中, 效率高低是最主要的竞争因素.

bilingual.source: Utmost efficiency in the design and manufacture, of turbomachinery is a prime competitive factor .
bilingual.target: 在涡轮机设计和制造中，效率高低是最主要的竞争因素。

bilingual.source: Under-explored and unbelievably alien, the hot zone planets are finally being recognized as prime space travel destinations.
bilingual.target: 未被探索和难以致信的外星人,热带区域的行星终会被认为是主要的太空旅行的目的地。

bilingual.source: The Prime Minister of Australia , said that "in terms of world well-being, Florey was the most important man ever born in Australia".
bilingual.target: 澳洲首相也说“从为人类造福的角度来讲，他是澳洲史上出世的最主要的人。”

bilingual.source: The conduct and behavior of the parties involved and especially that of the defaulting party is therefore a prime factor to be considered.
bilingual.target: 由此，合同和有关双方当事人，特别是违约方的行为和举动是主要的考虑因素。

bilingual.source: However, for the food industry, the prime goal is to obtain an enzyme which offers a high performance for the applications in question at an economic price.
bilingual.target: 但是，对于食品工业，主要的目标是获得一种在应用中具有较高活性并且价格经济的酶。

list.abstract: Prime是韩国星际争霸2的战队，于2010年10月13日成立。曾获得KSL2012冠军、GSTL2012第一赛季冠军。该战队在2015年12月2日正式解散。

yingyinNormal.en: Sentinel Prime. We bid you return.
yingyinNormal.zh: 御天敌，我们欢迎你回来。

yingyinNormal.en: Do I need to speak to the Prime Minister?
yingyinNormal.zh: 要我去跟总理谈谈吗？

yingyinNormal.en: And it was, Prime Minister. I can assure you.
yingyinNormal.zh: 那确实是，我能向您保证。

yingyinNormal.en: Ilsa Faust, Prime Minister. She disappeared 2 years ago.
yingyinNormal.zh: 首相大人，是伊尔莎·福斯特，她在两年前失踪了。

yingyinNormal.en: I am Optimus Prime and this message is to my creators.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我是擎天柱，这段信息是给我的造物主。

yingyinNormal.en: It is I, Optimus Prime. It is all right. You are safe.
yingyinNormal.zh: 是我，擎天柱，没事了，你安全了。

yingyinNormal.en: The only way to revive him, we needed Prime and his matrix.
yingyinNormal.zh: 能让他复活的唯一办法，就是擎天柱和矩阵。

yingyinNormal.en: We signed your peace treaty, Nova Prime. What more do you want?
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们签了和平协定，你还要怎样？

yingyinNormal.en: Yeah, I better get prime time, not one of these midmorning speeches.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我最好能拿到黄金时段，而不是在垃圾时段发表讲话。

yingyinNormal.en: I've given the Prime Minister my personal assurance you're on the case.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我亲自向首相保证你在积极破案。

yingyinNormal.en: What? It's prime real estate. Everything else in Williamsburg is taken.
yingyinNormal.zh: 怎么了，这可是风水宝地啊，星巴克在Williamsburg已经无孔不入了。

yingyinNormal.en: Who was this captain? The Great Sentinel Prime. The technology's inventor.
yingyinNormal.zh: 机长是谁？伟大的帮主，御天敌，发明这项技术的人。

yingyinNormal.en: Jia Sidao, the prime minister who vanquished the demon and saved the Song.
yingyinNormal.zh: 宰相贾似道，击败了魔鬼拯救了大宋。

yingyinNormal.en: At full capacity, it's the temporary home to more than 90,000 prime beef steers.
yingyinNormal.zh: 在全力运转的情况下，它能暂时容纳九万多头肉牛。

yingyinNormal.en: I'm afraid, Prime Minister, Director Hunley and I share responsibility for this.
yingyinNormal.zh: 首相，恐怕亨利局长和我都难辞其咎。

yingyinNormal.en: Cade, I am in your debt. My name is Optimus Prime. My Autobots. They're in danger.
yingyinNormal.zh: 凯德，我欠你一个恩情，我是擎天柱，我的博派伙伴有危险。

yingyinNormal.en: Wrist. You are to track down Optimus Prime, because you're the one human he trusts.
yingyinNormal.zh: 手腕，你要去跟踪擎天柱，人类之中他只信任你。

yingyinNormal.en: If you will follow Denarian Dey, he has something to show you. Thank you, Nova Prime.
yingyinNormal.zh: 请你们跟丹纳戴走，他带你们去看一样东西。谢谢总司令。

yingyinNormal.en: Chase Patterson, 25, his family slain in 2008. Chase was a prime suspect at the time.
yingyinNormal.zh: 切斯·帕特森，25岁，全家在2008年被杀害，切斯是当时的主要嫌疑人。

yingyinNormal.en: We get it when the bounty hunter gets Prime. Meanwhile, there has been a complication.
yingyinNormal.zh: 等地狱猎人抓到擎天柱就会有，不过现在事情变得有点麻烦 。

由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

sense_info_list.en: make something ready for use or action

examination_example.sentence: The action will <highlight>prime</highlight> your muscles for when you can get out there again.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 这个动作会让你的肌肉得到充分锻炼，以便你能重出江湖。

examination_example.sentence: Viewing a fast-food logo for just a few milliseconds <highlight>primes</highlight> us to read 20 percent faster.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 注视快餐标志仅几毫秒，可以让我们的阅读速度提高20%。

sense_info_list.en: first or highest in rank or importance

examination_example.sentence: Feasibility should be a <highlight>prime</highlight> concern in policymaking.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 可行性应该是政策制定的首要考虑。

sense_info_list.en: a state or time of greatest strength, vigor, or success in a person's life

examination_example.sentence: When Hoffa's Teamsters were in their <highlight>prime</highlight> in 1960, only one in ten American government workers belonged to a union; now 36% do.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 1960年，当霍法的卡车司机处于全盛时期时，只有十分之一的美国政府工作人员属于工会；现在有36%的人属于工会。

sense_info_list.en: of the best possible quality; having all the expected or typical characteristics of something

word_usage.usage: prime用作形容词时，本身已经含有“最”的意味，因此一般不用very修饰，也没有比较级和最高级形式。

prime多用作及物动词，prime sb. for/with sth.或prime sb. to do sth.，表示“使某人做好准备做某事”。例：
He primed her for her duties.
他事先让她熟悉了自己的任务。
